<footer class="footer">
  <div class="footer-inner">
    <div class="footer-brand">
      <img src="/logo.png" alt="South Florida Injury Centers — Chiropractic Physicians" class="footer-logo" />
      <p class="footer-tagline">Chiropractic evaluation and treatment for auto accident patients. Two locations serving Broward and St. Lucie County.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-cols">
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h4>Locations</h4>
        <p>5715 N. University Dr.<br/>Tamarac, FL 33321<br/>Broward County</p>
        <p style="margin-top:12px">1700 SE Hillmoor Dr., Suite 502<br/>Port Saint Lucie, FL 34952<br/>St. Lucie County</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h4>Services</h4>
        <a href="#services">Chiropractic Evaluation</a>
        <a href="#services">Spinal Manipulation</a>
        <a href="#services">Digital Radiography</a>
        <a href="#services">Clinical Documentation</a>
        <a href="#services">Physiotherapy Modalities</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h4>Contact</h4>
        <a href="tel:+19546066325">(954) 606-NECK — Tamarac</a>
        <a href="tel:+17723332648">(772) 333-2648 — Port Saint Lucie</a>
        <a href="#book" class="footer-cta">Schedule an Evaluation</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer-legal">
    <div class="footer-legal-inner">
      <p>This advertisement was generated by or on behalf of Brian Wilner, D.C. (Florida License #CH8052) and Kelly Kane, D.C. (Florida License #CH13758), licensed chiropractic physicians, South Florida Injury Centers. Licensed to practice chiropractic medicine only. Not licensed as medical doctors in the State of Florida. Treatment outcomes vary by patient. No results are guaranteed. The information on this website is for general informational purposes only and does not constitute medical or legal advice.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer-bottom">
    <p>© {new Date().getFullYear()} South Florida Injury Centers. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>Recover. Restore. Live.</p>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .footer {
    background: #0d2137;
    padding: 64px 24px 0;
  }
  .footer-inner {
    max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 2fr;
    gap: 64px; padding-bottom: 48px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(27,175,196,0.2);
  }
  .footer-logo {
    height: 68px; width: auto;
    filter: brightness(0) invert(1);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .footer-tagline {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .footer-cols {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 28px;
  }
  .footer-col h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--teal-light); margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .footer-col a, .footer-col p {
    display: block; font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    margin-bottom: 8px; line-height: 1.65; transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .footer-col a:hover { color: var(--white); }
  .footer-cta {
    display: inline-block !important; margin-top: 10px;
    background: var(--grad-teal); color: var(--white) !important;
    padding: 10px 16px; border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 600 !important; font-size: 0.8rem !important;
    transition: opacity 0.2s !important;
  }
  .footer-cta:hover { opacity: 0.88; }

  /* Legal disclosure — legible on dark bg */
  .footer-legal {
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(27,175,196,0.15);
    padding: 24px 0;
  }
  .footer-legal-inner {
    max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .footer-legal p {
    font-size: 0.775rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .footer-bottom {
    max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 18px 0;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    font-size: 0.775rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(27,175,196,0.1);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .footer-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 36px; }
    .footer-cols { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .footer-bottom { flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; text-align: center; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 480px) { .footer-cols { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
